<!-- vraag_01 -->
    <div id="vraag_01" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(25000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="25000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">Vraag 1</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"></p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<p>For accessibility assistance, which of the following programs is an on-screen keyboard?</p><br>
<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">xkb</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">atkb</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">GOK</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">xOSK</li>
</ul>


</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
